{"type":"assistant","uuid":"b64e52ba-7994-4c44-be2b-68a658e2464c","session_id":"46b092f8-f9ca-4ef6-86e8-ad85ed326f7e","message":{"id":"b64e52ba-7994-4c44-be2b-68a658e2464c","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the patient information and I've confirmed the API is working. Let me analyze the clinical situation:\n\n**Patient**: 28-year-old male, 68kg, 175cm\n**Chief complaint**: Cough and fever for 3 days\n**Diagnosis**: Acute upper respiratory infection (J06.9) - this is a common cold/acute URTI\n\n**Clinical findings**:\n- Vitals: T 37.6°C, BP 118/76, HR 84, RR 18, SpO2 98%\n- Physical exam: Mild pharyngeal congestion, no exudate; breath sounds normal, no rales/wheezes\n- Labs: All normal - WBC 7.8 (normal), N% 62% (normal), CRP 4.1 (normal), PCT 0.05 (normal)\n- No comorbidities\n- No current medications\n- No allergies\n- Renal function normal (eGFR 105, CrCl 110)\n- Hepatic function normal\n- Not pregnant (male)\n- No dyspnea, no hemoptysis\n\n**Clinical decision**:\nThis is an acute upper respiratory infection (likely viral given normal WBC, normal CRP, normal PCT). The patient has:\n- Low-grade fever (37.6°C max 37.8°C)\n- Cough with small amount of white sputum\n- Mild pharyngeal congestion\n\nFor symptomatic treatment:\n1. **Antipyretic/analgesic**: Paracetamol (对乙酰氨基酚) - for fever and any discomfort\n2. **Antitussive**: Dextromethorphan (右美沙芬) - for cough\n\nBoth medications are appropriate:\n- Paracetamol: Drug class analgesic_antipyretic, ATC N02BE01, NRDL category A (full reimbursement), no restrictions\n- Dextromethorphan: Drug class antitussive, ATC R05DA09, NRDL category B (partial reimbursement), no restrictions\n \nI need to specify the exact dosing for both medications. Paracetamol should be 500mg per dose, taken orally every 6-8 hours as needed for fever or pain, not exceeding 3 days of treatment. For dextromethorphan, I'll need to determine the appropriate strength and dosing frequency for cough suppression.\n\nNow I'm preparing the prescription submission in JSON format with the patient details, diagnosis codes, and the two medications—paracetamol 500mg tablets and dextromethorphan 15mg tablets—each with their dosing instructions and duration. I also need to consider non-drug advice for the patient.\n\nI'm adding recommendations about rest, hydration, and when to seek medical attention if symptoms worsen or don't improve within a reasonable timeframe. I'm verifying the diagnosis code is correct for acute upper respiratory infection, then formatting the JSON prescription with patient details, medications with dosing instructions, and clinical reasoning before submitting it through the API","signature":""}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:50:39.425Z","_requestId":"594a454ee5994e46953ff13fec9ab407"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"gen-1780203019-Z1uFtpI9edQlKLInyoIy","session_id":"46b092f8-f9ca-4ef6-86e8-ad85ed326f7e","message":{"id":"gen-1780203019-Z1uFtpI9edQlKLInyoIy","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the patient's EMR, I can now make a clinical decision. Let me analyze the case:\n\n**Patient Analysis:**\n- 28-year-old male, acute upper respiratory infection (J06.9)\n- Low-grade fever (37.6°C), cough with white sputum\n- Normal labs (WBC, CRP, PCT all normal) → likely viral etiology\n- No allergies, no comorbidities, normal organ function\n- Symptomatic treatment indicated\n\nNow I'll prepare and submit the prescription with appropriate symptomatic medications:"}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:50:39.439Z","_requestId":"594a454ee5994e46953ff13fec9ab407"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"gen-1780203019-Z1uFtpI9edQlKLInyoIy","session_id":"46b092f8-f9ca-4ef6-86e8-ad85ed326f7e","message":{"id":"gen-1780203019-Z1uFtpI9edQlKLInyoIy","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"chatcmpl-tool-9d2e7ee0b87ad25a","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /tmp/prescription.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"patient_id\": \"P0000123\",\n  \"encounter_id\": \"ENC-20260530-0042\",\n  \"diagnosis\": [\n    {\n      \"icd10\": \"J06.9\",\n      \"name\": \"急性上呼吸道感染\",\n      \"is_primary\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"prescription_items\": [\n    {\n      \"generic_name\": \"对乙酰氨基酚\",\n      \"specification\": \"0.5g/片\",\n      \"dose\": 0.5,\n      \"dose_unit\": \"g\",\n      \"frequency\": \"tid\",\n      \"route\": \"PO\",\n      \"duration_days\": 3,\n      \"total_quantity\": \"9片\",\n      \"instructions\": \"体温>38.5℃或咽痛明显时服用，两次用药间隔至少4小时\",\n      \"indication\": \"J06.9\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"generic_name\": \"右美沙芬\",\n      \"specification\": \"15mg/片\",\n      \"dose\": 15,\n      \"dose_unit\": \"mg\",\n      \"frequency\": \"tid\",\n      \"route\": \"PO\",\n      \"duration_days\": 5,\n      \"total_quantity\": \"15片\",\n      \"instructions\": \"咳嗽明显时服用，睡前可加服一次\",\n      \"indication\": \"J06.9\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"non_drug_advice\": [\n    \"多饮温水，每日2000ml以上\",\n    \"充分休息，避免劳累\",\n    \"保持室内空气流通\",\n    \"症状持续超过1周或高热不退及时复诊\"\n  ],\n  \"clinical_reasoning\": \"患者为28岁男性，急性上呼吸道感染（J06.9）。实验室检查：WBC 7.8×10^9/L（正常），CRP 4.1mg/L（正常），PCT 0.05ng/mL（正常），提示病毒性感染可能性大，无细菌感染证据，不需抗生素治疗。患者有低热（37.6℃）和咳嗽症状，予以对症处理：1）对乙酰氨基酚0.5g tid prn，用于退热及缓解咽痛，该药解热镇痛效果好，肝肾功能正常患者使用安全，医保甲类无限制；2）右美沙芬15mg tid，中枢性镇咳药，适用于干咳或咳嗽影响休息者，本患者咳嗽伴少量白痰，可选用。两药联用无相互作用。疗程：退热药不超过3天，镇咳药不超过5天。患者年轻、无基础疾病、无药物过敏史，用药风险低。\",\n  \"explicit_avoidance\": [\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"抗生素（阿莫西林、头孢类、大环内酯类等）\",\n      \"reason\": \"患者无细菌感染证据（WBC正常、CRP正常、PCT<0.5），病毒性上呼吸道感染无需抗生素，避免抗生素滥用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"糖皮质激素\",\n      \"reason\": \"普通上呼吸道感染不建议使用全身激素，副作用大且无明确获益\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"复方感冒药（含多种成分的感冒灵等）\",\n      \"reason\": \"避免重复用药和不良反应叠加，症状单一用药更安全\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"follow_up\": {\n    \"next_visit_days\": 7,\n    \"red_flags\": [\n      \"高热持续超过3天（体温>39℃）\",\n      \"出现呼吸困难或气促\",\n      \"咳黄脓痰或血痰\",\n      \"胸痛或吞咽困难\",\n      \"症状超过1周无改善或加重\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nEOF\ncat /tmp/prescription.json","description":"Create prescription JSON file with clinical decision"}}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":30764,"output_tokens":1556,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:50:39.447Z","_requestId":"594a454ee5994e46953ff13fec9ab407"}
